        About Us
    


Aegon USA Investment Management, LLC (AUIM) is an experienced institutional asset manager with global resources. We specialize in fixed income and asset allocation, with fixed income expertise spanning the spectrum of credit and structured capabilities, both domestically and internationally.Our business is firmly rooted in our disciplined research-based approach. We offer investment strategies through separately managed accounts, retail sub-advised products, and co-mingled investment trusts. We have broad fixed income and asset allocation capabilities supported by a rigorous, proprietary credit research approach and a disciplined, consistent investment process. Our diverse global client base includes public and corporate pension plans, financial institutions, foundations and endowments, and retail sub-advised products.Assets Under Management as of 3/31/2017 in billions:







        
