Mark Bloom
(1964, Nationality: American)
Global Chief Technology Officer and member of the Management Board, Aegon N.V.
Mark Bloom has over 30 years’ experience in information technology. He joined Aegon from Citi in February 2016, where he served as Global Head of Consumer Digital and Operations Technology.Read more >






